comment: /**  * To add a 3rd party Maven repository.  *  * @param name the repository name  * @param url  the repository url  */
code: /**  * To add a 3rd party Maven repository.  *  * @param name the repository name  * @param url  the repository url  */ void addMavenRepository(String name, String url).

comment: /**  * Downloads the artifact using the Maven coordinates and scans the JAR for Camel components  * which will be added to the CamelCatalog.  *  * @param camelCatalog          The Camel Catalog  * @param groupId               Maven group id  * @param artifactId            Maven artifact id  * @param version               Maven version  * @return the names of the components that was added, or an empty set if none found or they already exists in the catalog  */
code: /**  * Downloads the artifact using the Maven coordinates and scans the JAR for Camel components  * which will be added to the CamelCatalog.  *  * @param camelCatalog          The Camel Catalog  * @param groupId               Maven group id  * @param artifactId            Maven artifact id  * @param version               Maven version  * @return the names of the components that was added, or an empty set if none found or they already exists in the catalog  */ Set<String> addArtifactToCatalog(CamelCatalog camelCatalog, String groupId, String artifactId, String version).
